'''Dominic Guard''' ([[18 June|June 18]], [[1956]]) is a British actor. He voiced [[Peregrin Took]] in [[The Lord of the Rings (1978 film)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (1978 film)]]. He is the younger brother of [[Christopher Guard]], who voiced [[Frodo Baggins]].
